definition: the male organ of copulation (`member' is a euphemism)
details:
noun
- the male organ of copulation (`member' is a euphemism)
= synonyms: penis
- an external body part that projects from the body
= synonyms: appendage
- an organization that is a member of another organization (especially a state that belongs to a group of nations)
= example: an organization that is a member of another organization (especially a state that belongs to a group of nations)
- one of the persons who compose a social group (especially individuals who have joined and participate in a group organization)
= example: one of the persons who compose a social group (especially individuals who have joined and participate in a group organization)
= synonyms: fellow member
- anything that belongs to a set or class
= example: anything that belongs to a set or class
